{
  "texts": [
    "A demonstration of this error can be seen in Figure 10.",
    "Figure 10 shows the responses of ChatGPT-3.5 and ChatGPT-4 to question 5 in the national mathematics exam.",
    "After analyzing the answers provided by both versions, it was discovered that they were unable to consider all potential scenarios presented in the question and attempted to solve the problem without accounting for the land areas.",
    "The study's third sub-problem showed that ChatGPT-3.5 had difficulty employing upper and lower limits in problems with inequality.",
    "Additionally, it disregarded whole numbers when determining the value of a point on the number line, treating the distance between two points as one unit."
